                        ad consequatur in dolores culpa, dignissimos, eius non possimus fugiat. Esse ratione fuga, enim,
                        ab officiis totam.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!--Footer-->
            <div class="modal-footer justify-content-center">
                <a href="" type="button1" class="btn btn-danger">Get it now <i class="far fa-gem ml-1 text-white"></i></a>
                <a href="" type="button" class="btn btn-outline-danger waves-effect" data-dismiss="modal">No, thanks</a>
            </div>
        </div>
